### Description

So, the problem is ‚Äì how to properly set types of form with FormArray that contains FormGroup inside it?

```typescript
form = new FormGroup({
    control_one: new FormControl<string | null>(null),
    array_two: new FormArray<FormGroup>([]),
});
```

So FormArray has multiply FormGroup:

```typescript
arrayGroup = new FormGroup({
    value_one: new FormControl<number | null>(null),
    value_two: new FormControl<string | null>(null)
});
```

FormArray type cannot be set:

```typescript
interface ArrayGroupItem {
  value_one: FormControl<number | null>;
  value_two: FormControl<string | null>;
}

form = new FormGroup({
    control_one: new FormControl<string | null>(null),
    array_two: new FormArray<ArrayGroupItem>([]), // error
});
```


